🧠 HOW THE WHOLE SYSTEM RUNS (CODE FLOW)
Pseudocode:
def omop_pipeline(note):

    # 1. HF preprocessing
    entities = hf_ner(note)

    # 2. HF embedding retrieval
    candidates = hf_retrieve(entities)

    # 3. Ollama reasoning
    llm_output = ollama_llm(note, candidates)

    # 4. HF reranking
    final = hf_rerank(note, llm_output, candidates)

    # 5. validation
    return validate_omop(final)
